      "rdf:value": "<L>8345<pc>44,3<k1>anti<k2>anti<h>2<e>1\r\n<hom>2.</hom> <s>anti</s> ¦ <lex>f.</lex> an elder sister (in theatrical language), <ls>L.</ls> for <hom>1.</hom> <s>a/nti</s> See <ab>col.</ab> 2.<info lex=\"f\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
